msgid ""
"KDE Menu Edit lets you edit how your apps are presented in application "
"launchers, such as Plasma's Application Launcher widget."
msgstr ""
"Med KDE-menyredigering kan du redigera korleis programma dine skal "
"presenterast saman med andre, for eksempel i program­startaren i Plasma."
